cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >
  If you use this software, please cite it as below.
  Please also cite the foundational works listed under references.

title: "DOME Registry V2"
type: software
version: 2.0.0
date-released: "2026-04-30"
license: CC-BY-4.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/gavinf97/dome-registry-v2"

abstract: >
  DOME Registry V2 is a full-stack, Dockerised ML annotation registry.
  Researchers submit machine learning papers and an AI Copilot auto-fills
  a structured annotation form guided by the DOME checklist
  (Data, Optimisation, Model, Evaluation). The registry stores structured
  JSON annotations alongside full provenance metadata, with ORCID
  authentication, versioned history, and a moderation workflow.

authors:
  - family-names: Farrell
    given-names: Gavin
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0005-8810-545X"

keywords:
  - DOME
  - machine learning
  - reproducibility
  - annotation registry
  - bioinformatics
  - LLM
  - FastAPI
  - NestJS
  - Angular

